manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "blog"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "blog"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
askama_axum = "0.3.0"
axum-macros = "0.3.8"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
futures = "0.3.29"
hyperlocal = "0.8.0"
tower = "0.4.13"
tracing = "0.1.37"

[dependencies.askama]
version = "0.12.1"
features = ["with-axum"]

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.6.20"
features = ["macros"]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.31"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.188"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.7.1"
features = ["runtime-tokio", "tls-rustls", "postgres", "chrono", "uuid"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.32.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4.4"
features = ["fs"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.4.1"
features = ["v4", "serde"]
